So here's what showed up in your day:

You leaned {axis1.dominant} on agency — {axis1.insight}

On what you gave and expected, you showed {axis2.dominant} — {axis2.insight}

And when you stepped back to see the whole picture, your frame was mostly {axis3.dominant} — {axis3.insight}

That's not a judgment. It's just what you chose to notice today. Tomorrow you can choose again.

See you tomorrow.
